rdnb 0.1-1 [2017-02-14]
-----------------------

* data cleaning option added

* progress bar added (for limit="all" only)

* limitation for number of results (1-100) removed

* NOT-operator support added to publisher search

* new function "n_rec" added - get number of records

* new function "print_query" added - print search query

* other small fixes and improvements


